element.text: SORRY THAT IT TOOK SUCH A LONG TIME TO MAKE THIS GAME. PEOPLE HAVE BEEN REALLY MEAN TO ME AND MY MENTAL ISSUES MAKE ME TOO SAD TO DEVELOP THE GAME, BUT IF I TAKE MY MEDICINE THEN IM TOO TIRED TO DEVELOP THE GAME, SO EITHER WAY THE GAME DOESNT GET WORKED ON. AND MY FRIEND IS CURRENTLY BEING ABUSED BY HER FAMILY AND I HAVE BEEN SPENDING A LOT OF TIME TRYING TO SAVE HER. I THOUGHT SHE KILLED HERSELF MONTHS AGO BUT I JUST FOUND OUT SHES STILL ALIVE. ALSO MY JERK COUSIN YELLS ALL NIGHT LONG AND I CANT SLEEP BUT NOBODY CARES AND THEY JUST SAY ITS MY FAULT FOR LETTING HIM SWEAR AND SCREAM BOTHER ME. I AM BEING ABUSED AND NOBODY EVEN CARES. I AM TRYING MY BEST SO PLEASE JUST DONT JUDGE THE GAME TOO HARSHLY
WARNING: MASSIVE WALL OF TEXT AHEAD. SO YOU MAY BE ASKING YOURSELF,"WHY IS THIS GAME SO WEIRD". OR MAYBE YOU ARENT... WELL EITHER WAY
